# Aseprite Viewer Project Roadmap (Started: 2026-02-12)
Current Version: v33 (Stable) - GitHub Uploaded

## [CURRENT STATUS - v39]
- Viewport: 640x360 target resolution guide with darkened letterbox effect (Toggleable).
- Hybrid Profile System: Independent Player/NPC management.
- Combat: Max 2-stack combo buffering, Dash cancel, Multi-step movement.
- Movement: Adjustable Attack Forward physics.
- Camera: Vertical offset, Right-drag, Manual/Auto toggle.
- Playback: Full control (Pause, Step, Speed, Refresh).
- Hitbox: Slice visualization with persistent keys (H toggle).
- Watch Mode: Real-time Aseprite monitoring.
- Juice & VFX: Screen Shake, Dash After-images.
- Persistence: All settings (including Viewport) auto-saved via JSON.
- Layers: Individual layer visibility toggling.

